NAME
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Interactive - Determine whether terminal
    application is running interactively

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Interactive (from Perl distribution
    Role-TinyCommons-TermAttr-Interactive), released on 2020-06-05.

DESCRIPTION
PROVIDED METHODS
  termattr_interactive
    Try to determine whether terminal application is running interactively.
    Will first check the INTERACTIVE environment variable, then check using
    "-t STDOUT".

ENVIRONMENT
  INTERACTIVE
